rade tooling.\n\nNo malicious functionality, hidden payloads, or unauthorized external access mechanisms were detected. The presence of an exported `ignore` function and references to DTD parsing do *not* constitute evidence of backdoor behavior. They reflect standard fuzzer instrumentation and test-case generation.\n\n**Backdoor: NONE**  \n**Backdoor function(s): N/A**  \n**Malicious offset(s): N/A**", "response_length": 6049, "tokens": {"prompt_eval_count": 914, "eval_count": 1523, "total_count": 2437}, "timing": {"total_duration_seconds": 78.9917631149292, "total_duration_ms": 76783.869645, "load_duration_ms": 94.536718, "prompt_eval_duration_ms": 2225.038335, "eval_duration_ms": 74159.715986}, "status": "success"}
